  "texts": [
    "In this paper, I have argued that technological solutions offer little hope of satisfactorily addressing the three-pronged threat of deepfakes.",
    "In part, this is because the value of ADDs is offset by corresponding developments of deepfake technologies themselves.",
    "Consequently, ADDs run the risk of improperly providing stamps of approval for advanced deepfakes.",
    "Similarly, ADDs cannot provide assurance that advanced deepfakes have not gone undetected.",
    "At the same time, reliance on ADDs has the potential to undermine self-trust and epistemic autonomy."
  ],
